trans-unit.source: Configures a service credential.
trans-unit.target: Konfigurerer tjenesten legitimasjon.

trans-unit.source: Use this class to specify the credential for the service such as an X.509 certificate.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne klassen til å angi legitimasjonen for tjenesten som et X.509-sertifikat.

trans-unit.source: Also, use this class to specify the authentication model for various client credentials such as user name and password validation.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne klassen også for å angi godkjenning modellen for ulike klienten legitimasjon som bruker og passord validering.

trans-unit.source: This class is used as a parameter in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SecurityBindingElement.BuildChannelListenerCore%2A> method, by methods of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ServiceCredentialsSecurityTokenManager>, and is returned by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes som en parameter i den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SecurityBindingElement.BuildChannelListenerCore%2A>metoden av metodene for den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ServiceCredentialsSecurityTokenManager>, og er returnert av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ServiceCredentialsSecurityTokenManager> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SecurityBindingElement.BuildChannelListenerCore%2A>
